e%20whether%20the%20recent%20commissioning%20of%20four%20tech%20executives%20as%20part-time%20Army%20officers%20is%20in%20keeping%20with%20laws%20and%20practices%20against%20self-dealing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Democracy%20Defenders%20Fund%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcfce73f5-6016-42c8-9343-fa96f8863f56.usrfiles.com%2Fugd%2Fcfce73_98782732a33f4242a5b2e58f39ce6efc.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esent%20the%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20requesting%20that%20investigators%20determine%20%26quot%3Bwhether%20the%20assignment%20of%20these%20officials%20to%20the%20Army%20Reserve%20is%20consistent%20with%20the%20Federal%20conflict%20of%20interest%20laws%26quot%3B%20and%20whether%20their%20appointments%20qualify%20as%20%26quot%3Bmisuse%20of%20position%20and%20nonpublic%20information.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20executives%20%E2%80%94%20Shyam%20Sankar%2C%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20Palantir%3B%20Andrew%20Bosworth%2C%20chief%20technology%20officer%20of%20Meta%3B%20Kevin%20Weil%2C%20chief%20product%20officer%20at%20OpenAI%3B%20and%20Bob%20McGrew%2C%20an%20advisor%20at%20Thinking%20Machines%20Lab%20who%20was%20the%20chief%20research%20officer%20for%20OpenAI%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-execs-just-joined-the-army-boot-camp-not-required-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejoined%20the%20Army%20Reserve%20just%20weeks%20ago%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20men%20will%20forgo%20traditional%20three-month%20boot%20camp%20for%20a%20two-week%20crash%20course%20on%20Army%20history%20and%20basic%20military%20knowledge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20executives%20may%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20influence%20Army%20and%20Defense%20Department%20contracts%20as%20newly%20minted%20lieutenant%20colonels%20or%20share%20vital%20inside%20information%20to%20benefit%20their%20companies%2C%20which%20could%20increase%20the%20value%20of%20compensation%20like%20stock%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20unusual%20for%20civilians%20with%20expertise%20to%20bypass%20the%20most%20junior%20officer%20ranks%20for%20mid-level%20appointments.%20Historically%20that%20has%20most%20often%20included%20chaplains%2C%20veterinarians%2C%20and%20medical%20providers%2C%20career%20fields%20that%20require%20advanced%20degrees%20to%20join.%20The%20Army%20has%20made%20efforts%20to%20recruit%20more%20Americans%20with%20cyber%20and%20tech%20experience%2C%20though%20the%20four%20executives%20are%20the%20highest-profile%20enlistments%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Democracy%20Defenders%20Fund%20outlined%20special%20concerns%20regarding%20ongoing%20contract%20work%20Palantir%20and%20OpenAI%20have%20undertaken%20with%20the%20DoD%20recently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20common%20for%20military%20reservists%20to%20have%20civilian%20careers%20in%20the%20DoD.%20The%20problem%20with%20these%20tech%20execs%2C%20the%20group%20says%2C%20is%20the%20profound%20amounts%20of%20lucrative%20government%20contracts%20at%20stake%20for%20their%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20direct-commissioned%20tech%20executives%20got%20to%20skip%20Army%20basic%20training%2C%20designed%20to%20prepare%20soldiers%20for%20combat%20and%20service%20in%20uniform.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F686448233d5881a51c1c7d27%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20direct-commissioned%20tech%20executives%20got%20to%20skip%20Army%20basic%20training%2C%20designed%20to%20prepare%20soldiers%20for%20combat%20and%20service%20in%20uniform.%3Cp%3ESgt.%20Dustin%20D.%20Biven%2FUS%20Army%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSome%20of%20these%20individuals%20have%20significant%20personal%20financial%20stakes%20in%20their%20outside%20employers%2C%20including%20stock%2C%20stock%20options%2C%20restricted%20stock%20units%2C%20and%20performance-based%20bonuses%2C%20which%20they%20seem%20unlikely%20to%20divest%20for%20a%20part-t