career-life-fell-apart-one-year-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs'%3C%2Fa%3E%20sex-trafficking%20and%20racketeering%20trial%20said%20it%20has%20reached%20a%20verdict%20on%20all%20but%20one%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20note%20to%20US%20District%20Judge%20Arun%20Subramanian%20at%204%3A05%20p.m.%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20jurors%20said%20they%20have%20agreed%20on%20a%20verdict%20on%20all%20charges%20except%20the%20first%20count%2C%20racketeering%20conspiracy.%20They%20did%20not%20disclose%20the%20verdict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20four%20counts%20are%20related%20to%20the%20sex%20trafficking%20of%20the%20prosecution's%20key%20witness%2C%20R%26amp%3BB%20singer%20Cassie%20Ventura%2C%20as%20well%20as%20another%20one%20of%20Combs'%20exes%20who%20testified%20under%20the%20pseudonym%20%26quot%3BJane.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20to%20count%20one%2C%20we%20have%20jurors%20with%20unpersuadable%20opinions%20on%20both%20sides%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said%2C%20reading%20aloud%20from%20the%20jury%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20the%20second%20day%20of%20jury%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20asked%20the%20judge%20to%20give%20the%20jurors%20a%20version%20of%20the%20Allen%20charge%20%E2%80%94%20standard%20instructions%20for%20a%20deadlocked%20jury.%20Combs'%20defense%20attorneys%20said%20it%20was%20too%20early%20for%20the%20charge%2C%20and%20that%20the%20judge%20should%20just%20ask%20the%20jurors%20to%20keep%20deliberating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs'%20defense%20lawyer%20Marc%20Agnifilo%20said%20that%20because%20the%20jury%20had%20already%20reached%20verdicts%20on%20four%20counts%2C%20the%20judge%20didn't%20need%20to%20give%20them%20elaborate%20instructions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20that%20this%20is%20akin%20to%20the%20other%20situations%20where%20other%20trial%20juries%20have%20been%20deliberating%20for%20longer%20or%20as%20long%20and%20haven't%20reached%20any%20verdicts%2C%26quot%3B%20Agnifilo%20said%20in%20court.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20dispositive%20difference%20is%20this%20jury%20has%20already%20reached%20four%20verdicts%2C%20so%20I%20don't%20think%20that%20we%20need%20to%20do%20anything%20to%20move%20them%20along.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20jurors%20left%20for%20the%20day%2C%20to%20return%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20the%20judge%20urged%20them%20to%20continue%20deliberating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20your%20duty%20as%20jurors%20to%20consult%20with%20each%20other%20and%20to%20deliberate%20with%20a%20view%20to%20reaching%20an%20agreement%2C%26quot%3B%20Subramanian%20said.%20%26quot%3BEach%20of%20you%20must%20decide%20the%20case%20for%20himself%20or%20herself%2C%20but%20you%20should%20do%20so%20only%20after%20a%20consideration%20of%20the%20case%20with%20your%20fellow%20jurors%2C%20and%20you%20should%20not%20hesitate%20to%20change%20an%20opinion%20when%20convinced%20that%20it%20is%20erroneous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20his%20lawyers%20stood%20and%20packed%20their%20bags%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20trial%20day%2C%20Combs%2C%20wearing%20a%20beige%20sweater%20over%20a%20white%20button-down%20shirt%2C%20sat%20slumped%20in%20his%20chair.%20He%20stared%20ahead%20and%20tapped%20his%20fingers%20on%20his%20lap.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%20at%20one%20point%20turned%20from%20his%20seat%20at%20the%20defense%20table%20and%20gave%20a%20quick%2C%20confident%20nod%20to%20his%20mother%2C%20three%20daughters%2C%20and%20three%20sons%2C%20two%20rows%20behind%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20federal%20prosecutor%20Mark%20Chutkow%2C%20who%20is%20not%20involved%20in%20the%20case%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20jury's%20note%20%26quot%3Bsuggests%20that%20the%20jury%20has%20likely%20voted%20to%20convict%20on%20most%20if%20not%20all%20of%20the%20other%20charges.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20racketeering%20conspiracy%20charge%20is%20the%20most%20complex%20charge%20for%20the%20prosecution%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chutkow.%20%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20at%20least%20some%20of%20the%20jurors%20would%20vote%20to%20convict%20on%20that%20charge%20would%20suggest%20that%20the%20jurors%20were%20willing%20to%20convict%20on%20the%20other%2C%20more%20straightforward%20charges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-trial-jury-selection-complete-meet-jurors-sean-combs-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eeight-man%2C%20four-woman%20panel%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20which%20is%20in%20its%20second%20day%20of%20deliberations%2C%20appeared%20to%20home%20in%20on%20testimony%20given%20by%20Ventura%20earlier%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-diddy-combs-trial-striking-revelations-to-know-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECombs'%20jury%3C%2Fa%3E%20sent%20a%20note%20to%20the%20judge%20asking%20for%20testimony%20transcripts%20relating%20to%20four%20specific%20parts%20about%20Ventura's%20alleged%20sex%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20asked%20for%20copies%20of%20Ventura's%20testimony%20regarding%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcassie-ventura-sean-diddy-combs-intercontinental-hotel-assault-settlement-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EInterContinental%20Hotel%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Los%20Angeles%2C%20about%20an%20event%20at%20Cannes%2C%20and%20about%20a%20%26quot%3Bfreak%20off%26quot%3B%20with%20Daniel%20Phillip%2C%20a%20dancer%20who%20testified%20that%20he%20was%20recruited%20multiple%20times%20for%20Combs'%20sex%20performances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jurors%20also%20requested%20Phillip's%20own%20testimony%20about%20an%20encounter%20with%20Ventura%20in%20New%20York's%20Essex%20hotel%2C%20where%20Phillip%20said%20he%20believed%20Combs%20had%20physically%20beaten%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%2C%20defense%20attorneys%2C%20and%20Subramanian%20quickly%20determined%20which%20portions%20of%20the%20transcript%20they%20should%20send%20to%20the%20jury%20regarding%20Phillip%20and%20Cannes%2C%20where%20Ventura%20testified%20Combs%20threatened%20to%20publish%20videos%20of%20them%20having%20sex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20they%20spent%20much%20of%20the%20morning%20arguing%20over%20the%20scope%20of%20testimony%20regarding%20the%20InterContinental%20hotel%2C%20which%20sprawled%20over%20hundreds%20of%20pages%20of%20the%20trial%20transcript.%20Combs%20was%20infamously%20caught%20on%20the%20hotel's%20security%20camera%20beating%20Ventura%20in%20a%20hallway%2C%20in%202016%2C%20following%20a%20freak%20off%20sex%20performance%20with%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20officially%20got%20the%20case%20on%20Monday%20at%20around%2011%3A30%20am%20ET.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20just%2070%20minutes%20into%20the%20panelists%20weighing%20the%20charges%20against%20the%20hip-hop%20mogul%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-deliberations-interrupted-jury-concerns-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ejury%20sent%20the%20judge%20a%20note%3C%2Fa%3E%20complaining%20about%20one%20particular%20juror.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20a%20juror%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20the%20note%2C%20%26quot%3Bwho%20we%20are%20concerned%20cannot%20follow%20your%20honor's%20instructions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20note%20identified%20the%20juror%20as%20the%20one%20sitting%20in%20seat%20number%20three%2C%20a%2051-year-old%20Manhattan%20man%20and%20self-described%20scientist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20ultimately%20instructed%20the%20jurors%20of%20their%20duty%20to%20follow%20his%20instructions%20and%20continue%20deliberations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAny%20kind%20of%20jury%20chaos%20is%20typically%20considered%20a%20good%20sign%20for%20the%20defense%2C%20Chutkow%20previously%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20general%20matter%2C%20the%20more%20conflict%20and%20the%20more%20chaos%20occurs%20in%20a%20jury%20deliberation%20that%20spills%20out%20so%20that%20the%20court%20and%20the%20counsel%20know%20about%20it%20tends%20to%20be%20better%20for%20the%20defense%20because%20it%20could%20mean%20that%20a%20mistrial%20is%20looming%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chutkow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChutkow%20added%20that%20in%20high-profile%2C%20complex%20cases%20such%20as%20Combs'%20%26quot%3Byou're%20going%20to%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20differences%20of%20opinion%20and%20things%20get%20very%20hot%20in%20the%20jury%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20have%20very%20strongly%20felt%20feelings%2C%20and%20there%20can%20be%20circumstances%20where%20a%20juror%20folds%20up%20their%20arms%2C%20turns%20away%20from%20the%20others%2C%20and%20says%20'I%20don't%20want%20to%20talk%20with%20you%20guys%20anymore%2C'%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20processes%20that%20it's%20sort%20of%20up%20to%20the%20jury%20to%20self-regulate%20and%20to%20figure%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Chutkow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20jury%20convicts%20Combs%2C%2055%2C%20on%20the%20top%20charges%20of%20sex%20trafficking%20and%20racketeering%20conspiracy%2C%20the%20music%20tycoon%20could%20face%20up%20to%20life%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-trial-jury-sean-combs-sex-trafficking-racketeering-partial-verdict-2025-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1751403326000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F68643a8cf748d8c055f4c26d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiddy-trial-jury-sean-combs-sex-trafficking-racketeering-partial-verdict-2025-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20jury%20in%20Sean%20%26quot%3BDiddy%26quot%3B%20Combs'%20sex-trafficking%20trial%20said%20in%20a%20note%20that%20they've%20reached%20a%20verdict%20on%20all%20charges%20except%20one.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22litaliano%40insider.com%20(Laura%20Italiano%2CNatalie%20Musumeci%2CJacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A68%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22http