%20meeting%20would%20go%20on%20to%20alter%20not%20just%20two%20lives%2C%20but%20the%20very%20landscape%20of%20healthcare%20in%20the%20village%20he%20had%20once%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20met%20a%20patient%20whose%20blood%20pressure%20was%2020%2F150.%20During%20our%20conversation%2C%20he%20mentioned%20that%20he%20came%20from%20a%20rural%20area%20that%20lacked%20access%20to%20doctors.%20I%20got%20curious%20about%20his%20background%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20him%20more%20about%20where%20he%20was%20from.%20To%20my%20surprise%2C%20he%20said%20Khagaria%20%E2%80%94%20my%20own%20district%20in%20Bihar.%20That%20patient%20had%20come%20all%20the%20way%20from%20Bihar%20to%20Delhi%20%5B1%2C200%20kilometres%5D%20just%20for%20the%20treatment%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20revelation%20shook%20him.%20%E2%80%9CDespite%20the%20presence%20of%20world-class%20medical%20care%20in%20places%20like%20Delhi%2C%20there%20was%20still%20a%20lack%20of%20adequate%20services%20in%20my%20region.%20This%20experience%20lit%20a%20spark%20in%20me%20%E2%80%94%20a%20determination%20to%20work%20in%20my%20hometown%20and%20improve%20healthcare%20access%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Dr%20Rahman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20Dr%20Rahman%20was%20working%20in%20the%20non-invasive%20cardiac%20department%20and%20had%20a%20clear%20path%20ahead%3A%20a%20stable%2C%20high-paying%20career%20in%20the%20city.%20But%20that%20single%20conversation%20awakened%20something%20deeper%20%E2%80%94%20a%20pull%20towards%20home%2C%20where%20healthcare%20was%20not%20a%20business%2C%20but%20a%20lifeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20cities%2C%20healthcare%20is%20business%3B%20back%20home%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20survival%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20That%20became%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20his%20mission%3A%20to%20provide%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F291947%2Fdelhi-doctor-neurologist-quits-united-states-job-g