https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236549%2Fbihar-farmer-earns-lakhs-superfood-makhana-entrepreneur-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-cultivation-farming-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecollecting%20the%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20familiarising%20herself%20with%20the%20locals%E2%80%99%20cultural%20nuances.%20Only%20when%20the%20ice%20was%20broken%20could%20she%20broach%20the%20subject%20of%20a%20collaboration.%20But%20ever%20since%20bonds%20were%20forged%2C%20they%E2%80%99ve%20been%20going%20strong.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETake%20Mahesh%20%3Cem%3Eji%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20instance.%20He%E2%80%99s%20one%20of%20the%20500%20farmers%20who%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20Pratibha%20for%20years%20now.%20The%20payment%20is%20seasonal%2C%20Mahesh%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%20clarifies%2C%20adding%2C%20however%2C%20that%20he%20is%20earning%20more%20than%20he%20was%20previously%20getting%20when%20there%20were%20other%20middlemen%20involved.%20Pratibha%20corroborates%20the%20figure%20to%20be%20a%2030%20percent%20increase.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBefore%20we%20got%20associated%20with%20Pearl%20Mithila%20Makhana%2C%20we%20used%20to%20sell%20our%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eto%20some%20buyers.%20They%20would%20sell%20it%20locally.%20Now%2C%20our%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20reaching%20everywhere%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20%3Cem%3EMakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%20farming%20is%20the%20pride%20of%20Mahesh%20%3Cem%3Eji%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99s%20ancestral%20line%20%E2%80%94%20%E2%80%9CMy%20great-grandfather%20also%20did%20this.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20doing%20it.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fodia-creators-climate-change-11_11zon-1751027351.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pratibha's%20journey%20to%20starting%20Pearl%20Mithila%20Makhana%20involved%20experiences%20of%20wading%20into%20muddy%20waters%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20documenting%20the%20laborious%20process%20of%20collecting%20the%20makhana%20seeds%2C%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fodia-creators-climate-change-11_11zon-1751027351.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fodia-creators-climate-change-11_11zon-1751027351-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fodia-creators-climate-change-11_11zon-1751027351-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fodia-creators-climate-change-11_11zon-1751027351-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fodia-creators-climate-change-11_11zon-1751027351-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-457187%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPratibha%E2%80%99s%20journey%20to%20starting%20Pearl%20Mithila%20Makhana%20involved%20experiences%20of%20wading%20into%20muddy%20waters%20to%20engage%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20documenting%20the%20laborious%20process%20of%20collecting%20the%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%2C%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAugust%20to%20November%20is%20a%20busy%20time%20for%20him%2C%20as%20this%20is%20the%20period%20when%20the%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Eseeds%20are%20harvested.%20The%20rest%20of%20the%20year%2C%20farmers%20would%20see%20a%20lull%20in%20activity.%20But%20not%20anymore.%20Pratibha%E2%80%99s%20brand%20keeps%20them%20busy.%20Farming%20families%2C%20especially%20the%20women%2C%20are%20engaged%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20%3C%2Fem%3Epost-harvesting%20that%20unfolds%20at%20the%20factory%20outlet%2C%20where%20the%20seeds%20are%20sun-dried%20to%20render%20them%20a%20longevity%20to%20survive%20transport.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20seeds%20are%20graded%20using%20a%20sieve%20to%20separate%20them%20according%20to%20size.%20Then%20follows%20tempering%20to%20loosen%20the%20kernel%20within%20and%20have%20it%20pop%20out%20of%20the%20black%20coloured%20seed.%20The%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%20is%20then%20once%20again%20cleaned%20and%20hand-sorted%20%3C%2Fem%3Einto%20sizes%20and%20makes%20its%20way%20to%20you.%20A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288654%2Fhealth-benefits-of-superfood-makhana-fox-nuts-helps-in-weight-loss%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebestseller%20is%20the%20%3Cem%3Erasgulla%20makhana%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20measures%20around%2022%20mm%2C%20Pratibha%20notes%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20is%20a%20favourite%20of%20mothers%20who%20have%20young%20children.%20But%2C%20she%20points%20out%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20also%20the%20most%20difficult%20one%20to%20procure.%20In%20a%20100%20kg%20batch%20of%20%3Cem%3Emakhana%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%201%20kg%20turns%20out%20to%20be%20this%20size.%E2%80%9D%20The%20process%20is%20labour-intensive.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fmakhana-1-1751027908.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Rich%20in%20carbohydrates%2C%20fibre%2C%20plant-based%20protein%2C%20nutrients%20including%20magnesium%2C%20potassium%2C%20phosphorus%2C%20iron%20and%20zinc%2C%20makhana%20is%20a%20superfood%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fmakhana-1-1751027908.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fmakhana-1-1751027908-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Fmakhana-1-1751027908-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https