tack%2C%20my%20trainers%20at%20the%20gym%20were%20surprised%20and%20even%20shocked%20that%20I%20could%20have%20gone%20through%20something%20like%20this.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2%20months%20before%20the%20heart%20attack%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20the%20signs%20were%20there%20%E2%80%94%20just%20easy%20to%20ignore.%20I%20would%20often%20feel%20lightheaded%20after%20small%20physical%20movements%2C%20like%20walking%20from%20my%20car%20to%20the%20office%20building.%20But%20the%20dizziness%20would%20fade%20quickly%2C%20so%20I%20brushed%20it%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20other%20things%20too%20%E2%80%94%20a%20constant%20feeling%20of%20bloating%20that%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20think%20much%20of%20at%20the%20time.%20It%E2%80%99s%20only%20now%2C%20when%20I%20look%20at%20old%20photos%2C%20that%20I%20can%20see%20it%20clearly.%20My%20body%20had%20been%20trying%20to%20tell%20me%20something%20%E2%80%94%20I%20just%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20listening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsk%20ChatGPT%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Life%20was%20as%20good%20as%20could%20be%20until%20the%20heart%20attack.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2Ffeatured-img-9_11zon-1-1751272632-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F202