0opportunity%20to%20create%20a%20solution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20firm%20foothold%20in%20electronics%20and%20communication%2C%20he%20launched%20%E2%80%98Agua%E2%80%99%20in%202019%20under%20the%20parent%20company%2C%20Nara%20Technologies.%20The%20startup%20focused%20on%20developing%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F346774%2Fbengaluru-residents-saving-water-scarcity-rainwater-harvesting-recycle-greywayer-aerators-restrictors%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmart%20solutions%20for%20water%20management%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20Agua%E2%80%99s%20innovation%20are%20AI-enabled%20smart%20devices%20designed%20to%20track%2C%20manage%2C%20and%20optimise%20water%20usage%2C%20built%20to%20drastically%20cut%20bills%20and%20conserve%20the%20valuable%20resource.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20how%20the%20system%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20install%20our%20smart%20water%20metres%20on%20the%20water%20inlets%20of%20apartments.%20These%20metres%20have%20flow%20sensors%20that%20measure%20how%20much%20water%20is%20being%20used%20in%20real%20time.%20The%20data%20is%20then%20sent%20wirelessly%20to%20the%20cloud%2C%20and%20residents%20can%20view%20their%20daily%20usage%20on%20a%20mobile%20app.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-4-1750998942.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smart%20systems%20help%20ensure%20that%20no%20drop%20is%20wasted.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-4-1750998942.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F06%2FRohit-Nara-4-1750998942-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fu